name: Stargrail's Protector Dragon
desc: When a card or effect is activated that targets a monster(s) you control that is linked (Quick Effect): You can send this card from your hand or field to the GY; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that card. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 Normal Monster in your GY; Special Summon it in Defense Position to your zone a Link Monster points to. You can only use this effect of "Stargrail's Protector Dragon" once per turn.
